# File: stylesheets/ie.css.ab
# Purpose: Empty Compass IE override stylesheet placeholder in the default stylesheets/ output directory
# Dependencies: []

## Overview
An empty CSS file at the default Compass `stylesheets/` output directory. Contains only the standard Compass IE override welcome comment instructing how to import it via conditional comments. No IE-specific overrides have been authored.

## Interface
No exports. Empty placeholder stylesheet.

## Dependencies
No project-level dependencies.

## Implementation Notes
- 6 lines — only the Compass IE override comment, no actual CSS rules
- Located in the default Compass output directory at the project root
- Counterpart to `app/styles/ie.css` and `app/assets/css/ie.css` — all three are empty or near-empty
- The `stylesheets/` location is the Compass default output; the project uses `app/assets/css/` as its primary directory
